To maximize your score, combine two 'extracted' items of the *same* type (e.g., two magical extracts or two mundane extracts) to get a valuable +60 item. Avoid the 'filter' tool on solid ingredients, as it always creates negatively valued 'poorly-filtered' items. Also, do not mix magical and mundane extracts, as this lowers the value. The 'vial' tool does not work well on liquid or gas ingredients, resulting in 'botched extraction' and negative values. Stick to vialing solids and combining like extracts for the highest scores!

message: Focus on 'magical' ingredients! Using 'vial' on a 'solid, magical' ingredient yields a valuable extract (e.g., unicorn horn, sunstone, mandrake root). Using 'filter' on a 'gas, magical' ingredient (e.g., dragon's breath) also creates a valuable item. Aim for one magical and one mundane in the final combination, if possible, but other combinations of extracted and filtered liquids also worked.
